Package: bimResilience
Type: Package
Title: BIM Fisheries Resilience Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("L.T.", "Kell", email = "l.kell@bim.ie", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing fisheries resilience under climate change scenarios.
    Provides functions for stock assessment, forward projection, and scenario analysis
    for ICES stocks including data-rich, data-limited, and Nephrops functional units.
